Package: be-btrfs
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: iav <iav@users.noreply.github.com>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), btrfs-progs (>= 6.1), util-linux
Recommends: shellcheck
Homepage: https://github.com/iav/be-btrfs
Description: Boot Environment manager for btrfs
 Solaris-style boot environments for Linux systems using btrfs.
 Provides beadm-compatible interface: create, destroy, list,
 mount, unmount, rename, activate.
